<span class="header1">Business/Management paired with Public Service
(CG)</span>

<p>If you scored high in the "C" and "G" categories, you are people-
oriented. You have leadership ability and can persuade others. You
feel a responsibility to others. You probably want to work in ways
that can help your friends, your family, and your community.</p>
<p>Most occupations in this pairing require at least a bachelor's
degree. In some of these jobs, it helps to have a master's degree or
a Ph.D.</p>
